Class MovieSession

java.lang.Object
com.group18.model.MovieSession
public class MovieSession extends Object
Represents a movie session for a specific movie in a cinema hall. This class provides details such as the session's schedule ID, hall, time, and the number of available seats.

  • Field Details

    • scheduleId

      private int scheduleId
      The unique identifier for the schedule of the movie session. It is used to distinguish different movie session schedules.

    • hall

      private String hall
      The name or identifier of the cinema hall where the movie session takes place.

    • time

      private LocalTime time
      The time at which the movie session is scheduled to start.

    • availableSeats

      private int availableSeats
      Represents the number of seats currently available for this movie session. It indicates how many more attendees can be accommodated in the session's hall.
